title: Google\Cloud\ResourceManager\V3\ListProjectsRequest
name: ListProjectsRequest
description:
The request sent to the [ListProjects][google.cloud.resourcemanager.v3.Projects.ListProjects] method.

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.parent
params.description: Required. The name of the parent resource to list projects under. For example, setting this field to 'folders/1234' would list all projects directly under that folder.

params.name: data.page_token
params.description: Optional. A pagination token returned from a previous call to [ListProjects] [google.cloud.resourcemanager.v3.Projects.ListProjects] that indicates from where listing should continue.

params.name: data.page_size
params.description: Optional. The maximum number of projects to return in the response. The server can return fewer projects than requested. If unspecified, server picks an appropriate default.

params.name: data.show_deleted
params.description: Optional. Indicate that projects in the DELETE_REQUESTED state should also be returned. Normally only ACTIVE projects are returned.
